        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ". of our money. At this time the ordinary wages for a day’s labour was one denarius; so that the whole sum amounted to about four months’ wages of a day labourer. It is possible, however, the sum, which seems to us so small, may have been earnest-money.",
